<p>The <a href="http://www.claritygrader.com/"><strong>Clarity Grader</strong></a> isnâ€™t as sleek and stylish as the other graders, but itâ€™s a pretty amazing tool for digging into your content and <a href="/blog/ws/2014/08/07/improve-writing-skills">analyzing your writin</a>g.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="f616ea15-84d2-4d98-b8a3-9ab24a000ecd" data-langcode="en">
