<p>After watching one video, I continued to watch more. In a following video, ComicBookGirl19 discusses how she plans on making special, extra-long form videos detailing the history of various <em>Game of Thrones</em> houses. The videos would be on sale at Vimeo for $2.</p>
<p>I already knew from past videos that this YouTuber created really high-quality content, and I didnâ€™t hesitate for an instant to buy access to her new video on Vimeo.</p>
<p>Whatâ€™s also cool is that she even put those videos â€“ which I know took many, MANY hours of work â€“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v9q4Ht-W164">onto YouTube for free</a> after they were out for several months.</p>
