<p>Some extra quick general rules when it comes to button placement:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Donâ€™t put your social buttons too close to the navigation.</strong> You donâ€™t want to have users accidentally clicking share buttons when they are trying to do navigate someplace else.</li>
