<h2>3. CRM Skills</h2>
<p>Businesses are also looking for <strong>experts in Customer Relationship Management (CRM) software</strong>, which serves as an essential tool for virtually any company. <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/11/09/crm-for-small-business">CRM software</a> is used to organize and manage customersâ€™ various interactions with a company. CRM software helps bridge the gap between sales, marketing, and customer service. Popular CRM software includes Salesforce and Oracle.</p>
<h2>4. Mobile Marketing</h2>
<p>Mobile is on the rise and no one is powerful enough to stop it. If mobile marketing were Godzilla, weâ€™d be pretty screwed right about now.</p>
