<h2>5. Lead Nurturing</h2>
<p>As companies say <em>sayonara</em> to hard sales tactics and cold calls, they increasingly look to lead nurturing as a better sales solution. In the <a href="/blog/ws/2013/07/18/b2b-ppc-guide">B2B world</a>, most customer relationships today begin with content offers, then continue on with lead nurturing through the sales funnel. Lead nurturing is in super high demand, so employees with experience in this area should be sure to note it on their resume&#8217;s marketing skills list and <a href="/blog/ws/2015/03/17/8-reasons-i-hate-linkedin-ads">LinkedIn</a> profiles.</p>
